title: What is CS0432?
labels: All compiler errors have to be fixed

sections.title: Symptoms
content: You are seeing the following error in the console window:

sections.title: Cause
content: CS0432 is caused when you use "::" to the right of an identifier that is not an alias.

sections.title: Resolution
content: In order to fix the CS0432 you will need to replace the "::" for an "."
